                                        <i class="fas fa-circle me-2"></i>Secure data routing through certified network infrastructure: Data is transmitted over networks certified to meet stringent security and compliance standards, minimizing risks associated with insecure pathways.
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="ms-2 me-2">
                                        <i class="fas fa-circle me-2"></i>Real-time monitoring of data flows to ensure their integrity: Continuous tracking and analysis of data transfers detect anomalies or unauthorized activities, preserving data accuracy and confidentiality.
